thread.title: Arkansas' Greenlaw is SEC Freshman of the Week
thread.title_full: Arkansas' Greenlaw is SEC Freshman of the Week

author: Associated Press
title: Arkansas' Greenlaw is SEC Freshman of the Week
text:
FAYETTEVILLE, Ark. -- University of Arkansas freshman linebacker Dre Greenlaw has been named the Southeastern Conference Freshman of the Week.
Greenlaw was announced Monday as the winner of the award after making 16 tackles during the Razorbacks' four-overtime win over Auburn.
Greenlaw made 12 of the tackles during the second half and the overtime as Arkansas beat Auburn 54-46.
 Football College Men Associated Press
